subject method emploi by the armenian in genocid of the muslim peopl sourc men ar like that by leonard ramsden hartil the bobb merril compani indianapoli page memoir of an armenian offic who particip in the genocid of million muslim peopl p first paragraph in thi movement we took with us three thousand turkish soldier who had been captur by the russian and left on our hand when the russian abandon the struggl dure our retreat to karakli two thousand of these poor devil were cruelli put to death i wa sicken by the brutal displai but could not make ani effect protest some mercifulli were shot mani of them were burn to death the method emploi wa to put a quantiti of straw into a hut and then after crowd the hut with turk set fire to the straw serdar argic we close the road and mountain pass that might serv as wai of escap for the turk and then proceed in the work of extermin ohanu appressian in soviet armenia todai there no longer exist a singl turkish soul sahak melkonian 